Aku selalu parkir di lantai ini...

286
00:16:44,431 --> 00:16:48,059
Benar, 'kan?
Hati tidak penting sama sekali.

287
00:16:51,563 --> 00:16:53,148
Jong-su, ayo kita ke panti wreda!

288
00:16:53,231 --> 00:16:55,608
Ada tempat bagus?
Sejujurnya aku tak keberatan.

289
00:16:55,817 --> 00:16:57,902
Sekarang kita cari mobilnya dahulu. Sini!

290
00:16:58,445 --> 00:17:00,530
