291
00:17:10,248 --> 00:17:12,751
- Astaga.
- Aku naik taksi!

292
00:17:14,461 --> 00:17:17,422
- Sulit dipercaya.
- Kau bisa tertawa di situasi ini?

293
00:17:18,590 --> 00:17:20,550
Tentu. Bagaimana lagi?

294
00:17:21,092 --> 00:17:23,928
Astaga. Kau bukan main.

295
00:17:24,554 --> 00:17:27,307
Serumit apa pun pikiranmu,
ini tetap sulit dipercaya.

296
00:17:27,557 --> 00:17:29,934
- Astaga!
- Aku naik taksi.

297
00:17:39,986 --> 00:17:42,155
IBU

