409
00:23:25,832 --> 00:23:27,500
Dokter Ahn Chi-hong.

410
00:23:29,669 --> 00:23:30,878
Bersediakah...

411
00:23:31,879 --> 00:23:34,715
kau menerima cinta adikku?

412
00:23:42,682 --> 00:23:44,559
Kau baik-baik saja? Pasti sakit.

413
00:23:48,396 --> 00:23:50,148
