- Berengsek!

415
00:23:51,691 --> 00:23:52,733
- Hei!
- Apa? Kenapa?

416
00:23:52,817 --> 00:23:53,943
- Aku tak lakukan apa-apa.
- Hentikan!

417
00:23:54,026 --> 00:23:55,778
- Beraninya kau!
- Memalukan!

418
00:23:55,862 --> 00:23:58,114
