434
00:24:46,954 --> 00:24:48,873
Aku harus menemui Tuan Insting.

435
00:24:49,415 --> 00:24:52,293
Aku akan memberi hadiah kepadanya.

436
00:24:53,794 --> 00:24:55,046
Aku pergi.

